부모님께 선물을 보내요  (I'm sending it to my parents)

AVst 을까요 / ㄹ까요?
AVst: Action verb stem: used when asking the listener
his/her intention, opinion, or thoughts
The subject is the first person and can be omitted

양말 몇 켤레 드릴까요? (how many pairs of socks shall i give you?)
두 켤레 주세요 (give me two pairs please)
무엇을 살까요? (what should i buy)
이티셔츠를 사세요 (you should buy this t-shirt)
이 바지를 드릴까요? (shall i give you these pants?)
네, 주세요 (yes please)
몇시에 갈까요? (what time should i go?)
세 시에 오세요 (please come at 3)
언제 전화할까요? (when should i call)
내일 전화하세요 (please call me tomorrow)

